"favor, o copyright do autor da imaxe."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:112
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid ""
#| "On the second page, you can select the type of pieces into which the "
#| "image shall be sliced. &palapeli; comes with a collection of slicers "
